  "task_html": "<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WSbu3U3gB2M\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"video-link-card\" style=\"margin-bottom:16px;\">\n  <div class=\"video-link-icon\">&#x25B6;</div>\n  <div class=\"video-link-text\">\n    <div class=\"video-link-title\">Was ist eine Funktion?</div>\n    <div class=\"video-link-sub\">YouTube &middot; Einf&#xFC;hrung in den Funktionsbegriff</div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"video-link-arrow\">&#x2197;</div>\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"task-block task-blue\">\n  <div class=\"task-block-label\">Info: Funktion &amp; Wertetabelle</div>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 8px 0;\">Eine <strong>Funktion</strong> ordnet jedem x-Wert genau einen y-Wert zu. Die Zuordnungsvorschrift hei&#xDF;t <strong>Funktionsgleichung</strong>, z.&nbsp;B.:</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;font-size:16px;font-weight:800;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;margin:8px 0;\">f(x) = x + 2</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;margin:0;\">Damit berechnest du: f(1) = 1 + 2 = <strong>3</strong> &nbsp;|&nbsp; f(&minus;2) = &minus;2 + 2 = <strong>0</strong></p>\n</div>\n\n<p style=\"font-size:14px;margin:14px 0 8px 0;\"><strong>Aufgabe:</strong> F&#xFC;lle die Wertetabelle f&#xFC;r <strong>f(x) = x + 2</strong> aus.</p>\n\n<div class=\"tbl-wrap\">\n  <table>\n    <thead><tr><th style=\"background:#d95f2b;\">x</th><th style=\"background:#d95f2b;\">&minus;2</th><th style=\"background:#d95f2b;\">&minus;1</th><th style=\"background:#d95f2b;\">0</th><th style=\"background:#d95f2b;\">1</th><th style=\"background:#d95f2b;\">2</th><th style=\"background:#d95f2b;\">3</th><th style=\"background:#d95f2b;\">4</th></tr></thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td class=\"row-label\">f(x)</td>\n        <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"0\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n        <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"1\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n        <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"2\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n        <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"3\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n        <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"4\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n        <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"5\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n        <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"6\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"check-bar\">\n  <button class=\"btn-check\" onclick=\"checkStation(0)\">&#x2713; &#xDC;berpr&#xFC;fen</button>\n  <button class=\"btn-reset\" onclick=\"resetStation(0)\">&#x21BA; Zur&#xFC;cksetzen</button>\n  <span class=\"check-result\" id=\"check-result-0\"></span>\n</div>",
  "sol_html": "<div style=\"font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;line-height:2;\">\n  f(&minus;2)=<strong>0</strong> &nbsp;|&nbsp; f(&minus;1)=<strong>1</strong> &nbsp;|&nbsp; f(0)=<strong>2</strong> &nbsp;|&nbsp; f(1)=<strong>3</strong> &nbsp;|&nbsp; f(2)=<strong>4</strong> &nbsp;|&nbsp; f(3)=<strong>5</strong> &nbsp;|&nbsp; f(4)=<strong>6</strong>\n</div>"
}